Class RDFLoadToStudio

  • java.lang.Object
    • rdf.RDFLoad
      • rdf.RDFLoadToStudio
  • public class RDFLoadToStudio
extends RDFLoad
    Populates hashmaps of slides that can be displayed in the editor. Uses the data from the parent class' hashmaps as well in order to load a file back into the editor.
